divs: sighting detailsi was on my morning bike ride on 06\22\11 around 7:30 am i stopped to take a break, before i turned to go back home. i noticed the sun was very bright and peeking thru the clouds looked inspirational. i thought i would take a picture of it to post on my f.b for inspirational words on exersice. so when i came home i opened the picture to post and show my wife how pretty the sun was. it was then i noticed this oval amber light. i couldn't explain it, i thought maybe a reflection of the moon. my wife had said the moon wouldn't be over the sun. so i thought i would post it and see if i can find any corkey comments on my f.b. at school people said wow looks crazy i agreed. so i thought i would send it in and see if you guys had any leads or what you think. i called national ufo sightings and the guy was rude so i decided to bring the picure here instead. like i said i didn't know it was there at the time it didn't make a noise. if you look in the picture there is amber the reflects around the clouds as well.
Summary: Oval Amber shape cought on Camera in Crystal Lake il by the beach.
